{"id":"69af87bd80b5024be02f241c","title":"20260310","image":"https://gyazo.com/c89f4022efc2e124519e05c4ef19831f/raw","created":1773111234,"updated":1773111744,"lines":[{"id":"69af87bd80b5024be02f241c","text":"20260310","created":1773111234,"updated":1773111234},{"id":"69af87c10000000000784ec9","text":"#0310","created":1773111234,"updated":1773111234},{"id":"69af87c20000000000784eca","text":"","created":1773111234,"updated":1773111234},{"id":"69af87c30000000000784ecb","text":"ここで10年前の会話を","created":1773111236,"updated":1773111243},{"id":"69af87cc0000000000784ecf","text":"\t[https://gyazo.com/c89f4022efc2e124519e05c4ef19831f]","created":1773111244,"updated":1773111252},{"id":"69af87d40000000000784ed0","text":"\t\t提供: [igaiga555]","created":1773111252,"updated":1773111417},{"id":"69af88740000000000784ed2","text":"\t当時働いていた会社のコミュニケーションツールは [idobata] だったのだけど、そこで作ったbot(今でいう slash command や chat ops に近い感じだった気がする)になんだか忘れたけど会話する機能を雑にぶっこんだ....ような気がする","created":1773111412,"updated":1773111412},{"id":"69af885c0000000000784ed1","text":"\t[https://gyazo.com/ec6b77deb57888bab0f7613ebde15e02]","created":1773111389,"updated":1773111508},{"id":"69af88d30000000000784ed3","text":"\tあれから10年経って、今一番ヘビーユースなのは [Perplexity] なのだが、時事ニュースにアレコレ経緯を聞いたりしている","created":1773111508,"updated":1773111627},{"id":"69af894f0000000000784ed4","text":"\t\t最近 [Perplexity Computer] てのが出てきて、興味本位で Max に課金してみた","created":1773111631,"updated":1773111676},{"id":"69af897d0000000000784ed5","text":"\t\t1年前は [Devin] の月額課金をだいぶ渋ってたのを考えると、随分財布の紐が緩くなったというか、探索的になったなあとおもう","created":1773111677,"updated":1773111744},{"id":"69af87c30000000000784ecc","text":"","created":1773111236,"updated":1773111236},{"id":"69af87c30000000000784ecd","text":"","created":1773111236,"updated":1773111236},{"id":"69af87c30000000000784ece","text":"","created":1773111236,"updated":1773111236}]}